{"tid":2281752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★No IT】騰訊、阿里、美團 兩日市值蒸發1.98萬億，相當於10家 長和","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T14:14:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c54dfc62aa23a3f26c47f9c0b02360376934b55c","tid":2281752,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"「ATM」市值兩日蒸發兩萬億<br />\n<br />\n監管加劇，加上資金輪動至舊經濟板塊，科網股連日急跌，騰訊（0700）、阿里（9988）和美團（3690）兩日已分別累跌11.5%、14.4%、19.2%，單計「ATM」三股，市值在兩日間一共蒸發1.98萬億元，<span class=\"xx-large\">相當於近10家長和</span>（0001）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n科技股這次洗倉，除了因為疫苗有曙光，觸發這次資金輪動，由新經濟股轉投舊經濟股外，更因為<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>政府意欲出招打壓科技</strong></span>股壟斷情況。《反壟斷指南》共六章24條，當中涵蓋對於市場支配地位、不公平價格行為、低於成本銷售、限定交易、差別待遇（大數據殺熟）、搭售或附加不合理交易條件等行為的認定。此外，意見稿還特別提到VIE架構的經營者集中屬反壟斷審查範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/547684/atm%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84-%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E7%A7%91%E4%BC%81%E5%A3%9F%E6%96%B7-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E7%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%80%E7%B7%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F547684%2Fatm%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2580%25BC%25E8%2592%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E7%25A7%2591%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%25A3%259F%25E6%2596%25B7-%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E7%259C%258B%25E9%25AB%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25B7%259A&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=9fa7345b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/547684/atm%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E8%92%B8%E7%99%BC2%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84-%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E7%A7%91%E4%BC%81%E5%A3%9F%E6%96%B7-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E7%9C%8B%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%80%E7%B7%9A</a>"},{"pid":"3f7afa009c8800de4e1f1bb2279512